            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EThe%20Holy%20Spirit%20has%20come%20to%20dwell%20within%20us%20as%20the%20%22first%20installment%20of%20everything%20he%20will%20give%20us%22%20(2%20Corinthians%201%3A22)%2C%20or%20as%20the%20guarantee%20of%20our%20eternal%20inheritance%20(2%20Corinthians%205%3A5).%20He%20is%20the%20%22down%20payment%22%20of%20our%20heavenly%20inheritance%2C%20where%20we%20will%20receive%20the%20full%20manifestation%20of%20our%20sonship%20and%20adoption%20(Romans%208%3A19).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAll%20that%20happens%20to%20us%20in%20this%20life%20is%20%22training%20for%20reigning%2C%22%20mere%20preparation%20for%20the%20time%20when%20we%20will%20rule%20and%20reign%20with%20Christ%20Jesus.%20The%20Holy%20Spirit%20within%20us%20is%20our%20Helper%2C%20the%20One%20preparing%20us%20to%20reign%20with%20Christ.%20When%20we%20encounter%20spiritual%20attacks%2C%20the%20Holy%20Spirit%20helps%20us%20to%20pray%20and%20overcome.%20Therefore%2C%20everything%20we%20are%20going%20through%20now%20is%20simply%20maturing%20us%20and%20preparing%20us%20for%20dominion%20in%20eternity.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIf%20we%20have%20identified%20with%20Christ's%20sufferings%20and%20fought%20life%20through%2C%20the%20eternal%20day%20will%20come%20when%20we%20will%20share%20His%20glory.%20We%20will%20be%20seated%20on%20thrones%20with%20Him.%20%22I%20will%20invite%20everyone%20who%20is%20victorious%20to%20sit%20with%20me%20on%20my%20throne%2C%20just%20as%20I%20was%20victorious%20and%20sat%20with%20my%20Father%20on%20his%20throne%22%20(Revelation%203%3A21).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "2Chr.8:11-10:19",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E2%20Chronicles%208%3A11-10%3A19%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_8_11%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3ESolomon%20moved%20his%20wife%2C%20Pharaoh%26%23x2019%3Bs%20daughter%2C%20from%20the%20City%20of%20David%20to%20the%20new%20palace%20he%20had%20built%20for%20her.%20He%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BMy%20wife%20must%20not%20live%20in%20King%20David%26%23x2019%3Bs%20palace%2C%20for%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20been%20there%2C%20and%20it%20is%20holy%20ground.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_8_12%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Solomon%20presented%20burnt%20offerings%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20on%20the%20altar%20he%20had%20built%20for%20him%20in%20front%20of%20the%20entry%20room%20of%20the%20Temple.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_8_13%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20offered%20the%20sacrifices%20for%20the%20Sabbaths%2C%20the%20new%20moon%20festivals%2C%20and%20the%20three%20annual%20festivals%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20Passover%20celebration%2C%20the%20Festival%20of%20Harvest%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A13%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3EFestival%20of%20Weeks.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20the%20Festival%20of%20Shelters%26%23x2014%3Bas%20Moses%20had%20commanded.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_8_14%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20assigning%20the%20priests%20to%20their%20duties%2C%20Solomon%20followed%20the%20regulations%20of%20his%20father%2C%20David.%20He%20also%20assigned%20the%20Levites%20to%20lead%20the%20people%20in%20praise%20and%20to%20assist%20the%20priests%20in%20their%20daily%20duties.%20And%20he%20assigned%20the%20gatekeepers%20to%20their%20gates%20by%20their%20divisions%2C%20following%20the%20commands%20of%20David%2C%20the%20man%20of%20God.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_8_15%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3ESolomon%20did%20not%20deviate%20in%20any%20way%20from%20David%26%23x2019%3Bs%20commands%20concerning%20the%20priests%20and%20Levites%20and%20the%20treasuries.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_8_16%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Solomon%20made%20sure%20that%20all%20the%20work%20related%20to%20building%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20was%20carried%20out%2C%20from%20the%20day%20its%20foundation%20was%20laid%20to%20the%20day%20of%20its%20completion.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_8_17%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3ELater%20Solomon%20went%20to%20Ezion-geber%20and%20Elath%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A17a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%20(see%20also%202%26%23xA0%3BKgs%2014%3A22%3B%2016%3A6)%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3EEloth%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Elath.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20ports%20along%20the%20shore%20of%20the%20Red%20Sea%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A17b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20parallel%20text%20at%201%26%23xA0%3BKgs%209%3A26%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20sea.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20the%20land%20of%20Edom.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_8_18%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EHiram%20sent%20him%20ships%20commanded%20by%20his%20own%20officers%20and%20manned%20by%20experienced%20crews%20of%20sailors.%20These%20ships%20sailed%20to%20Ophir%20with%20Solomon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20men%20and%20brought%20back%20to%20Solomon%20almost%20seventeen%20tons%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A18%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E450%26%23xA0%3Btalents%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B15.3%26%23xA0%3Bmetric%20tons%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20gold.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_1%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E2%20Chronicles%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EVisit%20of%20the%20Queen%20of%20Sheba%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20queen%20of%20Sheba%20heard%20of%20Solomon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20fame%2C%20she%20came%20to%20Jerusalem%20to%20test%20him%20with%20hard%20questions.%20She%20arrived%20with%20a%20large%20group%20of%20attendants%20and%20a%20great%20caravan%20of%20camels%20loaded%20with%20spices%2C%20large%20quantities%20of%20gold%2C%20and%20precious%20jewels.%20When%20she%20met%20with%20Solomon%2C%20she%20talked%20with%20him%20about%20everything%20she%20had%20on%20her%20mind.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_2%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESolomon%20had%20answers%20for%20all%20her%20questions%3B%20nothing%20was%20too%20hard%20for%20him%20to%20explain%20to%20her.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_3%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20queen%20of%20Sheba%20realized%20how%20wise%20Solomon%20was%2C%20and%20when%20she%20saw%20the%20palace%20he%20had%20built%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_4%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3Eshe%20was%20overwhelmed.%20She%20was%20also%20amazed%20at%20the%20food%20on%20his%20tables%2C%20the%20organization%20of%20his%20officials%20and%20their%20splendid%20clothing%2C%20the%20cup-bearers%20and%20their%20robes%2C%20and%20the%20burnt%20offerings%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20and%20Syriac%20versions%20(see%20also%201%26%23xA0%3BKgs%2010%3A5)%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Eand%20the%20ascent.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Solomon%20made%20at%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_5%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EShe%20exclaimed%20to%20the%20king%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BEverything%20I%20heard%20in%20my%20country%20about%20your%20achievements%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A5%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eyour%20words.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20wisdom%20is%20true!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_6%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20didn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20believe%20what%20was%20said%20until%20I%20arrived%20here%20and%20saw%20it%20with%20my%20own%20eyes.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20had%20not%20heard%20the%20half%20of%20your%20great%20wisdom!%20It%20is%20far%20beyond%20what%20I%20was%20told.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_7%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EHow%20happy%20your%20people%20must%20be!%20What%20a%20privilege%20for%20your%20officials%20to%20stand%20here%20day%20after%20day%2C%20listening%20to%20your%20wisdom!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_8%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EPraise%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%2C%20who%20delights%20in%20you%20and%20has%20placed%20you%20on%20the%20throne%20as%20king%20to%20rule%20for%20him.%20Because%20God%20loves%20Israel%20and%20desires%20this%20kingdom%20to%20last%20forever%2C%20he%20has%20made%20you%20king%20over%20them%20so%20you%20can%20rule%20with%20justice%20and%20righteousness.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_9%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20she%20gave%20the%20king%20a%20gift%20of%209%2C000%20pounds%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E120%26%23xA0%3Btalents%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B4%2C000%20kilograms%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20gold%2C%20great%20quantities%20of%20spices%2C%20and%20precious%20jewels.%20Never%20before%20had%20there%20been%20spices%20as%20fine%20as%20those%20the%20queen%20of%20Sheba%20gave%20to%20King%20Solomon.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_10%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E(In%20addition%2C%20the%20crews%20of%20Hiram%20and%20Solomon%20brought%20gold%20from%20Ophir%2C%20and%20they%20also%20brought%20red%20sandalwood%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A10%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ealgum%20wood%3C%2Fem%3E%20(also%20in%209%3A11)%3B%20perhaps%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20%3Cem%3Ealmug.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Compare%20parallel%20text%20at%201%26%23xA0%3BKgs%2010%3A11-12.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20precious%20jewels.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_11%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20used%20the%20sandalwood%20to%20make%20steps%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A11%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Egateways.%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20meaning%20of%20the%20Hebrew%20is%20uncertain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20for%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20the%20royal%20palace%2C%20and%20to%20construct%20lyres%20and%20harps%20for%20the%20musicians.%20Never%20before%20had%20such%20beautiful%20things%20been%20seen%20in%20Judah.)%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_12%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EKing%20Solomon%20gave%20the%20queen%20of%20Sheba%20whatever%20she%20asked%20for%26%23x2014%3Bgifts%20of%20greater%20value%20than%20the%20gifts%20she%20had%20given%20him.%20Then%20she%20and%20all%20her%20attendants%20returned%20to%20their%20own%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_13%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ESolomon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Wealth%20and%20Splendor%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EEach%20year%20Solomon%20received%20about%2025%26%23xA0%3Btons%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20cl