%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20king%20made%20a%20huge%20throne%2C%20decorated%20with%20ivory%20and%20overlaid%20with%20pure%20gold.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_18%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20throne%20had%20six%20steps%2C%20with%20a%20footstool%20of%20gold.%20There%20were%20armrests%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20seat%2C%20and%20the%20figure%20of%20a%20lion%20stood%20on%20each%20side%20of%20the%20throne.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_19%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20were%20also%20twelve%20other%20lions%2C%20one%20standing%20on%20each%20end%20of%20the%20six%20steps.%20No%20other%20throne%20in%20all%20the%20world%20could%20be%20compared%20with%20it!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_20%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EAll%20of%20King%20Solomon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20drinking%20cups%20were%20solid%20gold%2C%20as%20were%20all%20the%20utensils%20in%20the%20Palace%20of%20the%20Forest%20of%20Lebanon.%20They%20were%20not%20made%20of%20silver%2C%20for%20silver%20was%20considered%20worthless%20in%20Solomon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20day!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr2_9_21%22%20bk%3D%22chr2%22%20ch%3D%229%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20king%20had%20a%20fleet%20of%20trading%20ships%20of%20Tarshish%20manned%20by%20the%20sailors%20sent%20by%20Hiram.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E9%3A21a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EHuram%2C%3C%2Fe